
            CCCCC  H    H    AA    L       I   SSSSS  TTTTTT  I
           C       H    H   A  A   L       I  S         TT    I
           C       HHHHHH   AAAA   L       I   SSSS     TT    I
           C       H    H  A    A  L       I       S    TT    I
            CCCCC  H    H  A    A  LLLLLL  I  SSSSS     TT    I
 
